%AI_Design_Template_for_Stand_Pouch
%Package_Lab_Epackage_Design_Template
%Japanese_Market_Standard_Dimensions

Template_Name: スタンドパウチ (Stand Pouch)
Product_Category: stand_up
Standard_Sizes:
  - 100mm x 160mm (Bottom 80mm)
  - 120mm x 200mm (Bottom 100mm)
  - 150mm x 240mm (Bottom 120mm)
  - 180mm x 280mm (Bottom 140mm)

Design_Specifications:
  - Bleed: 3mm on all sides
  - Safety Zone: 5mm from edges
  - File Format: Adobe Illustrator CS6 or later
  - Color Mode: CMYK
  - Resolution: 300 DPI
  - Bottom gusset included in dimensions

Cutting_Guides:
  - Solid line: Final cut line
  - Dashed line: Crease line for bottom formation

Design_Elements:
  [Front_Panel]
  - Product logo area: Top center
  - Product name: Below logo
  - Product description: Center area
  - Weight/Volume: Bottom left
  - Barcode area: Bottom right
  - Zipper closure indication: Below product name

  [Back_Panel]
  - Ingredients list: Top area
  - Instructions: Center area
  - Manufacturer info: Bottom area
  - Expiry date: Bottom right
  - Reusable closure instructions: Above zipper area

  [Bottom_Panel/Display_Side]
  - Additional branding elements
  - Promotional messages
  - "Stand here" indicator

Color_Guidelines:
  - Primary colors: Brand specific
  - Text color: High contrast (minimum 60%)
  - Background: Consider product visibility
  - Bottom panel: Can use contrasting color

Special_Features:
  - Zipper placement: 10-15mm from top
  - Hang hole option: Top center
  - Transparent window options
  - Matte/gloss finish areas

File_Naming_Convention:
  - Client_Project_ProductCode_Size.ai
  - Example: Epackage_Snacks_Brand_StandPouch_120x200.ai

